                  , no person being therein, about the hour of three in the afternoon, of the <rs id="t18030420-22-cd110" type="crimeDate">13th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-22-off109 t18030420-22-cd110"></join>, and stealing a silk cloak, value 2s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18030420-22-victim227" type="victimName">
                        Margaret 
                        May
                     <interp inst="t18030420-22-victim227" type="surname" value="May"></interp>
